name: little kit three - pink and green
description:
This little curated paper kit was specifically designed and compiled with Project Life in mind. A few small things to effortlessly blend into your stash and binder.

Please do keep in mind that some of the items in the kit are made from recycled materials and will sometimes have print on the back. Your understanding is greatly appreciated.

Each kit is bursting with:
one sewn doily card
one cutout chevron card
one blue glitter card
three other cards - clouds, green astro dots and a library ledger
one 3x4 sheet of washi tape
two round gift tags
three small assorted gift tags
two fold-over tabs
two heart paperclips
four sayings: "love this," "the story," "beautiful day," and a hashtag, "#omg"
